Third Department,

February, 1962

(February 2, 1962)

In decisions Nos. 1-4: Present — Bergan, P. J., Coon, Gibson, Herlihy and Reynolds, JJ.

(A) Jean D. Murnane, Appellant, v. Charles J. Murnane, Respondent. (B) Martin J. McEvilly et al., Respondents, v. James K. Camp, Appellant.

[In each action] Motions to dismiss appeals granted, by default, without costs.
